data.title: Hiten Tejwani and Gauri Pradhan celebrate their 11th wedding anniversary!

data.text:
Telly-town’s most sough after couple, Hiten Tejwani and Gauri Pradhan completed eleven wonderful years of togetherness today (April 29th).

The couple who made their television debut with Ekta Kapoor’s popular drama Kutumb appeared in Kyunki Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi, Kya Hadsaa Kya Haqeeqat, Kaisa YeH Pyar Hai, Left Right Left 2 and the most recent Meri Aashiqui Tumse Hi together. Fans from across the globe wished the happy couple on this joyous occasion.

https://twitter.com/theaish21/status/591053810585350144

The couple is making their return with Zee TV’s Rishton Ka Mela which began April 27th!

We wish the couple a happy anniversary. May they have many more to come!
